I'm Alastair Budge, and today we are going to be talking about The Meiji Restoration.

00:00:27.330 --> 00:00:31.620
It is the most amazing period of history when Japan completed an

00:00:31.679 --> 00:00:37.270
unbelievable transformation from feudal state to industrialised superpower.

00:00:37.799 --> 00:00:42.700
This is also a longstanding request from an amazing member, Taiki

